summary: So in dans recent video he said he’d be down to wear makeup
body:
So in dans recent video he said he’d be down to wear makeup

And he’s said the same in the past but just that he doesn’t really know how to use it.

And dnp have been hinting at a possible collab with safiya nygaard when they go to LA for VidCon (one can only hope). So like Phil’s channel seems very in line with safiyas content to me. Like I feel like he’d have a great time mixing a bunch of lipstick together or something and calling it a day.

But I was wondering literally what would dan post that safiya could be involved in. So like,,,

I just really wanna see Saf introduce Dan to the world of makeup. And Dan can overanalyse it like he does and talk about toxic masculinity and his relationship with it and I’m just,,,,

I’m very down for Danny boy in makeup

That’s all I have to say
